description:
Danny recaps his Watch What Happens Live experience behind the bar. He also recaps this week's Vanderpump Rules, which featured the firing of Tom Sandoval from best man duties, Ariana opening up about mental health, Scheana making her world famous enchiladas for one, Randall, and a winning side of Charli.
